src:
Lugn handelsdag i USA – men Ubers ras tilltog
Det blev en förhållandevis lugn tisdagshandel på Wall Street. Vid stängning hade S&P 500 backat 0,1 procent, Dow Jones stigit 0,1 procent medan Nasdaq stannade på nollan. Ubers aktie rasade 9,9 procent efter gårdagens svaga kvartalsrapport.
05 Nov 2019, 21:00 by Victor Hultgren

text:
Quiet trading day in the US - but Uber's race grew
It was a relatively quiet Tuesday trade on Wall Street. At closing, the S&P 500 had returned 0.1 percent, Dow Jones rising 0.1 percent while Nasdaq remained at zero. Uber's share plunged 9.9 percent after yesterday's weak quarterly report.
05 Nov 2019, 21:00 by Victor Hultgren
